creator: Hugh Lofting
description:
LibriVox recording of The Story of Doctor Dolittle (version 3) by Hugh Lofting.
Read in English by Karen Savage
After his parrot Polynesia teaches him to speak animal languages, Doctor Dolittle decides to abandon his human practice, and become an animal doctor. - Summary by Karen Savage
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

Download M4B (67MB)
